r entire repo, Slack, Jira, documentation, and PR history.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-03-10\",\n    \"category\": \"code agent\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\"Giving your agents the context to save time and tokens\", \"The context layer for AI-driven development\"]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Agent Skills\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.producthunt.com\",\n    \"description\": \"Finds and integrates skills for Claude Code, Cursor, Copilot and other AI coding tools. Part of the emerging Agent Skills open standard that allows AI coding assistants to perform agentic tasks.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-03-10\",\n    \"category\": \"AI coding CLI\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\"Agent skills follow an open standard across Claude Code, Cursor, and Copilot\"]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Pulldog\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.producthunt.com/products/pulldog\",\n    \"description\": \"A native macOS application for organizing code reviews from GitHub and GitLab. Provides a single place to monitor all code reviews with smart queries and filters. Connects to GitHub & GitLab and aggregates multiple accounts into one seamless inbox.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-03-08\",\n    \"category\": \"workflow agent\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\", \"Reddit\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": [\"A Mac app to keep your code reviews organized\", \"Connects to GitHub & GitLab for a unified code review inbox\"]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Claude Marketplace\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.producthunt.com\",\n    \"description\": \"Helps companies easily discover and acquire the AI tools they need for development workflows. Streamlines procurement of AI development tools.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-03-08\",\n    \"category\": \"workflow agent\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": []\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Clean Clode\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.producthunt.com\",\n    \"description\": \"Instantly cleans Claude Code and Codex terminal output. Improves readability of AI coding agent output in the terminal.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-03-02\",\n    \"category\": \"AI coding CLI\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": []\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Aura\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.producthunt.com\",\n    \"description\": \"Semantic version control for AI coding agents on top of Git. Provides versioning and tracking for AI-generated code changes.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-03-02\",\n    \"category\": \"workflow agent\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": []\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"CtrlAI\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.producthunt.com\",\n    \"description\": \"Transparent proxy that secures AI agents with guardrails. Provides security and governance for AI coding agents in production environments.\",\n    \"release_date\": \"2026-03-02\",\n    \"category\": \"workflow orchestration\",\n    \"sources\": [\"Product Hunt\"],\n    \"community_quotes\": []\n  }\n]\n",
