rce code, pull requests, documentation, chat systems, and production telemetry. Discussion includes context engineering, reconciling conflicting sources of truth, permission systems for AI, and shifting bottlenecks in the software development lifecycle.\",\n    \"author\": \"Dennis Pilarinos with Kevin Ball\",\n    \"source\": \"Podcast\",\n    \"url\": \"https://softwareengineeringdaily.com/2026/03/05/organizational-context-for-ai-coding-agents-with-dennis-pilarinos/\",\n    \"published_date\": \"2026-03-05\",\n    \"topics\": [\"AI coding agents\", \"organizational context\", \"context engineering\", \"Unblocked\", \"Agentic workflows\"],\n    \"type\": \"technical\"\n  }\n]\n",
