          "+                    <div class=\"update-description\">Now available in IntelliJ IDEA, PyCharm, WebStorm via Agent Client Protocol (ACP). Frontier models from OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Cursor.</div>",
          "+                    <div class=\"update-date\">2026-03-04</div>",
